      "type": "text",
      "data": "\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 1\">\n\t\t\t<table>\n\t\t\t\t<tbody><tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"border-width: 0pt; border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">\n\t\t\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-width: 0pt;\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"layoutArea\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"column\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">Mou </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">和 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">MacDown </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">是我在 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">Mac </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">下 过的两款优秀的 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">Markdown </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">编辑 。之前 直使 的是 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">Mou</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">，但 知怎\n的最近 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">Mou </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">在保存时总有 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">4s </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">以上的卡顿，这让我很 爽，没找到有效的解决 法，于是我被迫去寻找其它\n的 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">MD </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">编辑 。我尝试过很多种，但总觉得没有 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">Mou </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">体验好，最终让我找到  </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">MacDown——OS X</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">下开放\n源代码 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">Markdown </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">编辑 。\n</span></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<pre><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">背后的故事\n很有兴趣关注 这两款软件的作者及背后的故事，发现很有趣，在评测两款软件之前我们先   故事吧。\n</span></pre>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">Mou </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">的作者罗晨，个 主 :</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">http://chenluois.com/</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">，现居住天津， 由职业者。</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">MacDown </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">的作者</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">Tzu-ping\nChung</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">，个 主 :</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">https://uranusjr.com/</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">，现居住台 市，应该是台湾同胞吧。\n</span></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">根据 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">MacDown </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">作者的介绍，他曾经 度是 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">Markdown </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">的重度 户， 使 的编辑 基本是 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">Mou</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">，但 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">Mou\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">可以处 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">fenced code blocks</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">，却对代码 亮  持，同时在渲染 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">Markdown </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">时也有 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">bug</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">，这让他很苦恼。\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">Mou </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">的作者当时正准备转 该软件， 直没有 新，所以，他就开始从头开始模仿 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">Mou </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">写 个，因为是\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">Markdown editor for Macs</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">，所以取名为 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">MacDown</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">。\n</span></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">MacDown </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">作者 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">Chung </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">在征得 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">Mou </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">作者 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">Luo </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">的同意使   </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">Mou </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">的 款主题，发布  </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">MacDown </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">的原始版\n本。</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">Luo </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">最后发现 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">MacDown </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">时，很 愤，并指责 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">Chung </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">是 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">copycat</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">，意思是 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">MacDown </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\"> 寨  </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">Mou</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">。\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">Chung </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">也意识到确实是  抄袭  </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">Mou </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">很多东 ，根据某条推 的建议(并 是</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">Luo</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">发布的)，将之前\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">github </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">中项 描述 改成 :\n</span></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">MacDown is an open source Markdown editor for OS X, released under the MIT License. The author stole\nthe idea from Chen Luo’s Mou so that people can make crappy clones. ^1\n</span></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\"> 较详细的情节可以参  </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">Chung </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">的博客。 于 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">MacDown </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">和 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">Mou </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">的关系是怎样的，是 是 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">MacDown </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">就是\n 道德地克   </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">Mou </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">呢?这个每个 都有  的看法，这 就 讨论 。\n</span></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">欣喜的是， 前两款软件都找到  的发展模式，</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">Mou </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">已经完成 众筹，即将发布 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">1.0 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">版本，如果有对 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">Mou\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">有情怀的同学可以 持作者;</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">MacDown </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">依旧会   开源的道 。\n</span></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">Chung </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">的  话也道出 我的 声:<br>\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">Let’s focus on making better software for everyone. </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">好 ， 卦完 ，最后我要对两位作者表示由衷的谢\n</span></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<pre><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">意，贡献给我们好 的软件!下 我会根据我体验，分别提 下两款软件各 的特 地 。\n</span></pre>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">共同功能\n</span></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">提供丰富的简洁  好看的主题，同时 持 定义 提供丰富的渲染 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">Markdown </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">之后的 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">CSS </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">样式，同时 持\n 定义样式 英 单词的 动补全功能，按下 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">Esc </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">键 出补全的 表 字符、单词统计功能  持 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">fenced code\nblocks TeX </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">数学公式的 持  持导出 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">HTML </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">和 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">PDF </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">两种格式  捷的快捷键操作 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">... Mou </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">特 功能\n</span></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">集成 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">Tumblr </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">和 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">Scriptogr.am </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">发布博 \n</span></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"border-width: 0pt; border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">\n\t\t\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t</tbody></table>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 2\">\n\t\t\t<table>\n\t\t\t\t<tbody><tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"border-width: 0pt; border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">\n\t\t\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-width: 0pt;\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"layoutArea\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"column\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">可以配置 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">Tumblr </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">和 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">Scriptogr.am </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">的邮箱，在 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">Mou </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">上写 章通过 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">File-&gt;Post-&gt; </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">可以发布到这两个平台上， \n常  。\n</span></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">Mou </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\"> 持集成 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">Tumblr </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">和 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">Scriptor.am </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">语  持\n</span></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">Mou </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">内置 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">CJK </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">字符 持，你可以很容 使 中 、  、韩 等来写 章，同时还 持竖排的 格。\n</span></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">Mou </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\"> 持 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">CJK </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">及竖排 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">MacDown </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">特 \n</span></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">代码 亮\n</span></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">Mou </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">和 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">MacDown </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">都 持 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">fenced code blocks</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">(前后三个反引号可以表示代码块)，但 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">MacDown </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\"> 持加语\n 标识符实现代码 亮，这对程序员来说简直是福 啊， 常棒的功能。\n</span></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">MacDown </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\"> 持代码 亮 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">GFM Task List </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\"> 持\n</span></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">MacDown </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\"> 持 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">Task list</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">，有 这个功能，你可以将你的 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">MD </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">编辑   变成 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">TODO list</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">，是 是很赞?\n</span></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">MacDown </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">对 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">Task list </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">的 持 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">Jekyll Front-matter </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\"> 持\n</span></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">很多 使  </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">Jekyll </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">作为博客引擎，这时 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">Jekyll </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">的前 那段该怎么去渲染呢?</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">MacDown </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">和 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">github </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\"> 样可以 \n持。\n</span></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">MacDown </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">对 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">Jekyll front-matter </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">的 持 总结\n</span></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">OK</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">，总结完 ，如果 是 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">Mou </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">在我的 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">Mac </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">上有卡顿，我也没想着要换 款编辑 ， 前我在  </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">MacDown\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">感觉还是很 错的，因为有代码 亮 持就 以把我 下 。 于你选哪 款，你可以下载下来  体验体\n验，反正软件都很 。也许你跟我 样，因为某个 瑕疵放弃某个软件， 因为某个 功能的惊喜 喜欢上\n某个软件。\n</span></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">作者:   影 链接:</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">http://www.jianshu.com/p/6c157af09e84 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\"> 源:简书 著作权归作者所有。商业转载请\n联系作者获得授权， 商业转载请注明出处。\n</span></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">要到设置 打开 亮选项才  </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">preferences - rendering - Syntax highlighted code block</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">，把这个勾上，然后\n选择你喜欢的主题。 然后那个任务清单的实现，也是需要勾上 个</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Helvetica'\">Task list syntax</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'PingFangSC'\">选项才 哦。\n</span></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"border-width: 0pt; border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">\n\t\t\t\t\t</td>